data.value: Hey! I was thinking that Drifloon is friendly enough to take me to somewhere entertaining!

data.name: Drifloon_0
data.value: Fwooo!

data.name: Slowking_0
data.value: Good luck on your journey!

data.name: SlowpokeL_0
data.value: The beach settlement is at east of the castle, and I heard the monkey fella has a map that has where the dungeon is.

data.name: SlowpokeR_0
data.value: Hey, Fetch me some snacks, will ya? We're excessively lethargic to help you...

data.name: Espurr_0
data.value: Oh there you are, I was so worried about you.

data.name: Vitaro_0
data.value: Go inside the castle to speak with the king because the king wants you there.

data.name: Minccino_0
data.value: We'll miss you, friend, I think you'll be traveling a lot after chatting.

data.name: Minccino_1
data.value: We'll be heading back to our home to rest.

data.name: Vitaro_1
data.value: Okey Dokey! I'll be waiting outside here.

data.name: Vitaro_2
data.value: Let's talk to the king! It's be easy!

data.name: Slowking_1
data.value: Ah, Just as I though. What I chose you has come.

data.name: Slowking_2
data.value: Before I begin to explain what transpired, may I ask as to the name of your team?

data.name: Slowking_3
data.value: So... your team name is [color=#FFA5FF]{0}[color], right?

data.name: Slowking_4
data.value: Listen now to my words, It is written in the Book of our god:

data.name: Slowking_5
data.value: Natzu fought powerful forces ages ago, and then the new, cruel god rebelled against authority.

data.name: Slowking_6
data.value: The darkness has concealed numerous locations, making it appear as though they do not exist, giving Natzu no chance..

data.name: Slowking_7
data.value: Now [color=#FFA5FF]{0}[color] and Vitaro...

data.name: Slowking_8
data.value: We need your assistance to recover, undo what they did, and bring peace to our world.

data.name: Slowking_9
data.value: May the light shine upon you, little soldiers.

data.name: Vitaro_3
data.value: Come on, Let's split up and find the source of what causes them! See ya!

data.name: Message_0
data.value: Let's not go in there, It's too dark and frightening...

data.name: Pichu_1
data.value: YYYAAAAHHHHHHH!!!!

data.name: Message_1
data.value: It looks like Pichu is being taken by the Drifloon.

data.name: Powwene_0
data.value: I'm sorry! When I heard the scream, I thought, Oh my god, I should have arrived earlier!

data.name: Powwene_1
data.value: It appears as though they were heading west...! This amusing little park must have been altered by them.

data.name: Powwene_2
data.value: Come on! I'll go with you! I can't let this get away.

data.name: Nidoqueen_2

data.value: Hey!

data.value: You again!?
